’Щ@a4442b4445341a25add036ff747817d87f02e64333352f2f45728b69bc73a88eЩҜTitle: title: par-each
Path: Flags
Content:
``--threads, -t {int}``
: The number of threads to use.
``--keep-order, -k``
: Keep sequence of output same as the order of input.
